@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### 1. 商品上架 - 成功 (201 Created)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "深入理解Java虚拟机",
  "description": "JVM经典书籍，深入剖析Java虚拟机原理",
  "price": 79.00,
  "stock": 100,
  "category": "计算机",
  "author": "周志明",
  "isbn": "978-7-111-50001"
}

### 2. 商品上架 - 第二本 (201 Created)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "领域驱动设计",
  "description": "DDD经典之作，领域驱动设计核心思想",
  "price": 99.00,
  "stock": 50,
  "category": "计算机",
  "author": "Eric Evans",
  "isbn": "978-7-111-50002"
}

### 3. 商品上架 - 名称为空 (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "price": 10.00
}

### 4. 商品上架 - 单价为空 (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试商品",
  "price": null
}

### 5. 商品上架 - 单价为0 (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试商品",
  "price": 0
}

### 6. 商品上架 - 单价为负数 (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试商品",
  "price": -1.00
}

### 7. 查询商品 - 成功 (200 OK)
# 将 1 替换为实际上架后返回的 id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

### 8. 查询商品 - 不存在 (404 Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/99999

### 9. 按名称搜索商品 (200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?name=Java

### 10. 按名称搜索商品 - 无匹配 (200 OK, 空数组)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?name=不存在的书

### 11. 按分类搜索商品 (200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?category=计算机

### 12. 按分类搜索商品 - 无匹配 (200 OK, 空数组)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?category=未知分类

### 13. 无参数搜索 (200 OK, 空数组)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### 14. 库存入库 +20 (200 OK)
# 将 1 替换为实际商品 id
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 20
}

### 15. 库存出库 -30 (200 OK)
# 将 1 替换为实际商品 id
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": -30
}

### 16. 库存出库 - 库存不足 (409 Conflict)
# 将 1 替换为实际商品 id
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": -99999
}

### 17. 库存变更 - 商品不存在 (404 Not Found)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/products/99999/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 10
}
